ore drugs that may result in moderate inhibition of CYP450 3A4 and moderate to potent inhibition of CYP450 2D6 is considered contraindicated in CYP450 2D6 extensive metabolizers (EMs) and intermediate metabolizers (IMs).', NULL, NULL, 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic');
