 used with eliglustat in any patient regardless of their CYP450 2D6 metabolizer status.', 'Metabolism', 'The use of eliglustat with a potent CYP450 3A4 inhibitor is considered contraindicated in CYP450 2D6 poor metabolizers (PMs) and intermediate metabolizers (IMs).', NULL, NULL, 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic');
